data.description: Take a look at this beautiful custom built home in the Twin Creeks development. Located at Tims Ford Lake in Winchester, TN. This property is a true example of modern living, with new construction and high-end finishes throughout. With four spacious bedrooms, along with a bonus room, this home offers ample living space for any family.  Step inside and experience the height of luxury with an outdoor kitchen and more. The indoor kitchen is equipped with stainless appliances, gorgeous granite countertops, and custom cabinets. Gated community, 3 pools, firepits, clubhouse, walking trails, boat slips, event venue, concerts, marina, on-site waterfront restaurant, community & general store.
